Property Features:
-  Large Living & Dining Area
- Upgraded Flooring Throughout
- Upgraded Kitchen (Siemen appliances) & Guest Powder Room
- En-suite Large Bedroom Suite
- 3 Bedrooms with Sea Views 
- Sea Views From Living / Dining Room
- Private Parking
- 2 Large Balconies
- High Ceilings 
- Can Be Purchased Partly Furnished
- 4,843 Sqft 
- Incredibly well priced Less than 1,000 AED a Sqft for sea View penthouse
This is the ideal family home for someone who wants to live in a luxurious apartment without paying a hefty price tag.']
